data.description: *** Sellers have an assumable Va loan for qualified and eligible buyers: Interest rate at 2.25 % and a $800,000 balance, roughly 60-day close***Nestled in Fillmore Place of West Alexandria, this chic 4-level end unit townhome seamlessly blends modern living with convenience. The lower level welcomes you with a spacious rec room, half-bath, and a 2-car garage with EV charger.  The second level boasts an open concept design featuring a well-appointed kitchen, light-filled living and dining rooms, and a dry bar. Upstairs, two generous bedroom suites await on the third level, accompanied by convenient laundry facilities with full-sized washer and dryer. The fourth level completes the package with a third bedroom suite, a versatile loft space, and an outdoor patio with a retractable awning and a double-sided gas fireplace—perfect for indoor / outdoor entertaining or enjoying your private retreat. Located near parks, shops, and restaurants, this townhome offers the ideal blend of style and functionality for a vibrant lifestyle. Schedule your showing today to experience the epitome of modern living.   Harris Teeter (0.7 mi), Target (1.2 mi), World Market (1.3 mi), Inova Alexandria Hospital (1.4 mi), Fort Ward Park (1.5 mi), Barcroft Park (1.8 mi), Shirlington Dog Park (1.8 mi).  Convenient to I-395, Leesburg Pike / Rt 7, Duke St / Rt 236, I-495, Van Dorn Metro (4.1 mi), Amazon HQ2 (5.5 mi), Downtown DC (7.2 mi).
